high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the coffee maker across the room.
Pick up the coffee cup in front of the coffee maker.
Turn to your right and go to the freezer.
Place the coffee cup in the bottom of the freezer for a moment, wait for it to chill, then remove the coffee cup from the freezer.
Step back from the refrigerator and move over to your right so that you are in front of the bottom cabinet to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the coffee cup in the bottom cabinet, to the right of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold coffee cup in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the coffee maker.
Take the mug from the coffee maker.
Turn right, go forward to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge. Take the mug from the fridge.
Move back from the fridge, face the fridge.
Put the mug in the bottom cabinet to the right of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the left, go across the room to the coffee maker.
Pick up the white mug that is on the coffee maker.
Turn around, hang a left and go to the fridge.
Put the mug inside the fridge and close the door, remove the mug once it is cold.
Turn around, go forward, turn around to face the cabinets and fridge.
Put the mug in the cabinet to the right of the fridge, just to the right of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug in a cabinet.
